description.standard: Here are the tracks on everyone's mind and in everyone's ears. From ballads to bops, pop to hip-hop to R&B and more, these are the biggest hits anywhere and everywhere—an ever-changing snapshot of now. Our editors are constantly searching for new music and updating this mix—so if you hear a song you like, add it to your library.
description.short: The biggest songs in pop, hip-hop, R&B, and more.
